content: I've been using Ibotta and Fetch Rewards for a while now, and I've been pretty happy with the cashback I've earned. But I do shop online at Walmart fairly frequently, so the 2% cashback from Walmart+ could be a nice addition. I think I'll crunch some numbers and see if it's worth it for me. Speaking of cashback, do you know if Walmart+ has any restrictions on earning cashback, like certain items or brands that aren't eligible?
